'''吸血鬼蟹屬'''（{{lang|la|'''''Geosesarma'''''}}），又名'''陸相手蟹屬'''<ref name=e-info>{{cite web |url=http://e-info.org.tw/node/91247 |title=海岸泥灘地的蟹兵日記 |author=[[施習德|施習德]] |language=zh-hant |date=2013-09-17 |accessdate=2014-06-10 |archive-date=2016-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708123339/http://e-info.org.tw/node/91247 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，是[[短尾下目|短尾下目]][[方蟹總科|方蟹總科]][[相手蟹科|相手蟹科]]以下的一個[[屬_(生物)|屬]]。本屬之前被劃歸[[方蟹科|方蟹科]]，今從相手蟹科。本屬物種體形細小，其[[頭胸甲|頭胸甲]]寬度不超過{{convert|10|mm|1}}<ref name="Hartnoll">{{cite book |author=Richard G. Hartnoll |chapter=Evolution, systematics, and geographical distribution |editor=Warren W. Burggren & Brian R. McMahon |year=1998 |title=Biology of the Land Crabs |publisher=[[Cambridge_University_Press|Cambridge University Press]] |isbn=9780521306904 |pages=6–54 |url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=RR09AAAAIAAJpg=PA35 }}{{dead link|date=2018年2月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。本屬物種會在淡水或陸上生活，但在繁殖時無需返回海裡，被認為是真正的陸生蟹<ref name="Schubart03">{{cite journal |author=Christoph D. Schubart, Hung-Chand Liu & José A. Cuesta |year=2003 |title=A new genus and species of tree-climbing crab (Crustacea: Brachyura: Sesarmidae) from Taiwan with notes on its ecology and larval morphology |journal=[[Raffles_Bulletin_of_Zoology|Raffles Bulletin of Zoology]] |volume=51 |issue=1 |pages=49–59 |url=http://rmbr.nus.edu.sg/rbz/biblio/51/51rbz049-059.pdf |access-date=2014-06-10 |archive-date=2012-02-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120206205011/http://rmbr.nus.edu.sg/rbz/biblio/51/51rbz049-059.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

出沒於[[印度|印度]]<ref>{{cite web |author=S. K. Pati, M. K. Dev Roy & R. M. Sharma |date= |accessdate=2012-08-11 |title=Freshwater crabs |work=Checklist of Indian fauna |publisher=[[Zoological_Survey_of_India|Zoological Survey of India]] |url=http://zsi.gov.in/checklist/freshwater_crabs.pdf |format=[[PDF|PDF]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130917025112/http://zsi.gov.in/checklist/freshwater_crabs.pdf |archivedate=2013-09-17 }}</ref>、到[[東南亞|東南亞]]一帶，遠至[[所羅門群島|所羅門群島]]及[[夏威夷|夏威夷]]亦可找到牠們的踪影<ref name="Hartnoll"/>。

